keyFacts: The document is a DOJ OIG Investigations Division transcription request form dated May 31, 2022.
It requests transcription of a 48-minute, 35-second audio interview related to case number 2019010614.
The estimated transcription cost was $208.08 with an actual cost of $158.95.
The form includes references to Special Agent in Charge, Special Agent, Attorney, and Office of the Chief Medical Examiner (OCME).
The case agent's duty station is listed as NYFO (likely New York Field Office).
